  "detailed_description": "In 1592, Japan invaded the Joseon on Korean Peninsula, initiating the Imjin War. <br>Despite eventually repelling the Japanese forces after a long and arduous conflict, Joseon fell into disarray due to the aftermath of the war. <br>Bandits emerged across the land, and corrupt officials exploited the chaos to plunder the people.<br><br><strong>In an effort to rectify this situation, an unnamed Seonbi embarked on the path.</strong><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/fc73092b841d24adca7b9a2f8fe2e8bd.poster.avif?t=1726530236\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/fc73092b841d24adca7b9a2f8fe2e8bd.webm?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/fc73092b841d24adca7b9a2f8fe2e8bd.mp4?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Seonbi: Scholar of Joseon is a side-scrolling action game developed with the historical backdrop of Korea. <br>As a player, you will encounter bandits, remnants of the Japanese forces, and monsters on your journey.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/e59f6f303febc49b8b2aaa508fccd9c5.poster.avif?t=1726530236\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/e59f6f303febc49b8b2aaa508fccd9c5.webm?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/e59f6f303febc49b8b2aaa508fccd9c5.mp4?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Using a bow as your primary weapon and a variety of skills and items inspired by the weaponry of the Joseon era, you must strategically utilize them to defeat enemies and reach Hanyang (modern-day Seoul).<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/d294bc78f1a7cab580401fad248dc68a.poster.avif?t=1726530236\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/d294bc78f1a7cab580401fad248dc68a.webm?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/d294bc78f1a7cab580401fad248dc68a.mp4?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Seonbi: Scholar of Joseon is designed to fluidly connect short actions, enabling players to string together combos and experience the thrill of direct combat.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/0bdc4e16ab74a0061f98bc3c2f725b34.poster.avif?t=1726530236\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/0bdc4e16ab74a0061f98bc3c2f725b34.webm?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/0bdc4e16ab74a0061f98bc3c2f725b34.mp4?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Equip yourself with your unique skills and item combinations, assist the citizens in dire situations, and journey to Hanyang to rectify the chaos that plagues Joseon!",
  "about_the_game": "In 1592, Japan invaded the Joseon on Korean Peninsula, initiating the Imjin War. <br>Despite eventually repelling the Japanese forces after a long and arduous conflict, Joseon fell into disarray due to the aftermath of the war. <br>Bandits emerged across the land, and corrupt officials exploited the chaos to plunder the people.<br><br><strong>In an effort to rectify this situation, an unnamed Seonbi embarked on the path.</strong><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/fc73092b841d24adca7b9a2f8fe2e8bd.poster.avif?t=1726530236\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/fc73092b841d24adca7b9a2f8fe2e8bd.webm?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/fc73092b841d24adca7b9a2f8fe2e8bd.mp4?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Seonbi: Scholar of Joseon is a side-scrolling action game developed with the historical backdrop of Korea. <br>As a player, you will encounter bandits, remnants of the Japanese forces, and monsters on your journey.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/e59f6f303febc49b8b2aaa508fccd9c5.poster.avif?t=1726530236\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/e59f6f303febc49b8b2aaa508fccd9c5.webm?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/e59f6f303febc49b8b2aaa508fccd9c5.mp4?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Using a bow as your primary weapon and a variety of skills and items inspired by the weaponry of the Joseon era, you must strategically utilize them to defeat enemies and reach Hanyang (modern-day Seoul).<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/d294bc78f1a7cab580401fad248dc68a.poster.avif?t=1726530236\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/d294bc78f1a7cab580401fad248dc68a.webm?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/d294bc78f1a7cab580401fad248dc68a.mp4?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Seonbi: Scholar of Joseon is designed to fluidly connect short actions, enabling players to string together combos and experience the thrill of direct combat.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/0bdc4e16ab74a0061f98bc3c2f725b34.poster.avif?t=1726530236\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/0bdc4e16ab74a0061f98bc3c2f725b34.webm?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1925860/extras/0bdc4e16ab74a0061f98bc3c2f725b34.mp4?t=1726530236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Equip yourself with your unique skills and item combinations, assist the citizens in dire situations, and journey to Hanyang to rectify the chaos that plagues Joseon!",
